title: Anyone know a good oce site for coaching?
body:
im doing my best to practice myself but there are things im quite clearly lacking on, and frankly i learn alot more by asking questions than i do by reading guides online.

So really im just looking for recommendations of websites i can throw some money at to get some one on one time with high elo players to get taught shit.

replies.body: i could help u out for free if u want

This beast has already added me

ill be slightly less bronze in no time
give me asl's i might help you
2 years late can anyone give me a hand?
i can help u if u want to learn mid and some ad champs. other then that im clueless
